NAME nil/int tpt.decorations_enable(boolint state)
DESCRIPTION Toggle decorations.
LINK #tpt.decorations_enable
DETAILS
Toggle drawing decorations.

The number argument can be either 0 or 1, where 1 will enable decorations, and 
0 will disable them. If you don't pass in any arguments, the command will return
an integer, either 0 or 1, about whether decorations are turned on at the given 
moment.
